{"tid":1225981,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實林鄭都幾撚自我中心","createTime":"2019-06-15T09:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:19:36.000Z","uid":152432,"like":94,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2fbcbe166366c919fb70541a0f233d673bec1249","tid":1225981,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"啲人講警察濫權拉人，過度使用暴力，製造白色恐怖但佢永遠撻落堆'示威者'掟磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問佢點處理班被拉咗嘅人佢就即刻劃分界線，話唔關我事唔會干擾執法機關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講會唔會落台同會唔會道歉又因為自己自尊心成日表揚自己為香港好同有初心，永唔永再拉自己呀仔落水想博同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問佢點回應百萬人嘅遊行，佢就永遠撻出點都有人支持呢個論點同台灣夫婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總括而言，呢條女永遠只係諗自己啱人地錯，永遠唔識反省覺得成個香港有虧於佢，唔啱聽嘅說法同社運就唔理唔回應搞到事件滾大，當然仲有嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">串鳩在場講事實得罪佢嘅記者，串完爽完繼續遊花園無視人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"98b0e79bea9e165d48f5f154acf289b1cf79aeda","tid":1225981,"uid":99365,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:14:40.000Z","msg":"佢跟本就係個極小氣又冇料到嘅臭八"},{"pid":"8003e9202e64607beb28bd415ee54de20adf1332","tid":1225981,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98b0e79bea9e165d48f5f154acf289b1cf7